 false

(inner) ProfileContent(props) → {JSX.Element}

Description:

  • Renders the content of a user's profile page.

Example
return (
  <ProfileContent username="johnDoe" />
)
Parameters:
Name Type Description
props Object

The component props

Properties
Name Type Description
username string

The username of the profile to display
Returns:

Returns one of the following:

  • A loading skeleton while data is being fetched
  • An error message if fetching fails
  • A "private profile" message if the profile is not visible
  • The full profile presentation component with user data and profile strength metrics
Type
JSX.Element

JSX.Element

(require("profile"))(props) → {JSX.Element}

Description:

  • A component that displays a profile strength indicator with a progress bar and checklist.

Parameters:
Name Type Description
props Object
Properties
Name Type Description
profileStrength Object

Object containing profile strength information

Properties
Name Type Description
color string

CSS color class for the strength indicator
strength number

Percentage value (0-100) of profile completion
label string

Text label describing the profile strength level
hasProfile boolean

Indicates if user has added a profile photo
hasAbout boolean

Indicates if user has added an about section
hasSkills boolean

Indicates if user has added skills
hasEducation boolean

Indicates if user has added education
hasExperience boolean

Indicates if user has added experience
hasConnections boolean

Indicates if user has made connections
Returns:

A profile strength component with progress bar and checklist

(inner) ProfileContent(props) → {JSX.Element}

Description:

  • Renders the content of a user's profile page.

Example
return (
  <ProfileContent username="johnDoe" />
)
Parameters:
Name Type Description
props Object

The component props

Properties
Name Type Description
username string

The username of the profile to display
Returns:

Returns one of the following:

  • A loading skeleton while data is being fetched
  • An error message if fetching fails
  • A "private profile" message if the profile is not visible
  • The full profile presentation component with user data and profile strength metrics
Type
JSX.Element

Component props

Properties

 false

Callback function to remove the skill

Flag indicating if the remove operation is in progress

(inner) ProfileContent(props) → {JSX.Element}

Description:

  • Renders the content of a user's profile page.

Example
return (
  <ProfileContent username="johnDoe" />
)
Parameters:
Name Type Description
props Object

The component props

Properties
Name Type Description
username string

The username of the profile to display
Returns:

Returns one of the following:

  • A loading skeleton while data is being fetched
  • An error message if fetching fails
  • A "private profile" message if the profile is not visible
  • The full profile presentation component with user data and profile strength metrics
